[[File:Barracks_256.png|right]]The '''Barracks''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It increases the maximum army size of a city. Also increases the recruitment speed of all bordering [[Training Ground]]s, [[Stable]]s, [[Moonglow Tower]]s, [[Trinsic Temple]]s, [[Workshop]]s and [[Shipyard]]s.

Requirements: [[Town Hall]] Level 4

